             -REE_270 or _OSD_ROTATE_DEGREE_180
  87          //                enumOsdRotateMapA    -> _OSD_MAP_A_REMAPPING_DISABLE or _OSD_MAP_A_REMAPPING_ENABLE
  88          //                ucMapARowSize        -> MapA Row size
  89          //                enumOsdRotateMapB    -> _OSD_MAP_B_REMAPPING_DISABLE or _OSD_MAP_B_REMAPPING_ENABLE
  90          //                ucMapBRowSize        -> MapB Row size
